---
description: Enforce internal linking coverage and 2-click reachability in page body content.
globs: **/*.vue, **/*.html
alwaysApply: false
---

- Enforce two rules for body-content links:
- No orphaned pages: every page must have at least one inbound internal link.
- 2-click rule: every page must be reachable from home in 2 body-content clicks or fewer.

- Exclusions (do not count for compliance):
- Links in `header` or `footer`.
- Nav links that are part of header/footer navigation.

- Required flag format:
- 🚩 Orphaned page
- 🚩 2-click rule violation
- 🚩 2-click rule unverifiable
- ⚠️ Undeclared page linked
- ✅ Compliant

See `.cursor/skills/internal-linking-policy/SKILL.md` for full audit procedure and suggestion patterns.
